machine_configurations lists the machines and who is the top watchdog
and script scheudler

top machine
  schedule new tasks
  watch if any machine goes down
   if any machine goes down, mark its scripts as dead, ensure if it comes back it stops its scripts
  run applications
   mark applications as running when run
   mark applications as completed when completed

seconady machines
  watch top to see if it goes down
   if it goes down, select a a new top machine, ensure top machine does not consider itself top anymore
  run applications
   mark applications as running when run
   mark applications as completed when completed

could there be a list of must run processes (the scheduler) and
that it should be run on the first runner machine that can
handle it.
